### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("jwt", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Listar todas las familias
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/families
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Listar familias por norma
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/families?standard=AISC
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Listar perfiles (paginado, 20 por pagina)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Buscar perfiles por texto
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?q=IPE&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Filtrar perfiles por norma
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?standard=AISC
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Filtrar perfiles por tipo de forma y norma
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?shapeType=H&standard=AISC
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Filtrar perfiles por codigo de familia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?familyCode=W
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Busqueda combinada de perfiles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?q=IPE&standard=EURO&page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Obtener perfil por ID (reemplazar UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Listar items de catalogo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Buscar items por texto
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items?q=Hex
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Filtrar items por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items?itemType=FASTENER
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Busqueda combinada de items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items?q=Hex&itemType=FASTENER
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Obtener item por ID (reemplazar UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Listar tipos de item (paginado, scope organization)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Obtener tipo de item por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Crear tipo de item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tornilleria",
  "description": "Tornillos, tuercas, arandelas",
  "schemaDefinition": null
}

### Actualizar tipo de item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tornilleria - Inoxidable",
  "description": "Tornilleria en acero inoxidable",
  "schemaDefinition": null
}

### Eliminar tipo de item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/item-types/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Subir imagen a perfil (multipart, reemplazar UUID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/image
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="perfil.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
--boundary--

### Eliminar imagen de perfil
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/image
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Subir imagen a item (multipart, reemplazar UUID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/image
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="item.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
--boundary--

### Eliminar imagen de item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/image
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Servir imagen (GET público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/images/profiles/test-image.jpg
